        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple Watch X 结构改变，将采用较薄电路板物料</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/apple-watch-x-rcc-motherboard-rumors/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-watch-x-rcc-motherboard-rumors</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/apple-watch-x-rcc-motherboard-rumors/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 03:45:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手表]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple watch]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RCC]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231797</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>天风国际证券分析师郭明𫓹去年曾经撰文，预计在 2025 年推出的 iPhone 17 Pro，Apple 可能会采用树脂涂层铜（RCC）的主板。这款主板采用了薄膜铜物料，并且在外层覆盖树脂，整体主板设计因此变得更加轻薄。</p><p><span id="more-1231797"></span></p><p>根据台湾媒体 Digitimes 的最新报导，有供应链消息来源指至少一款下一代 Apple Watch，亦有可能使用上述的树脂涂层铜主板。由于这款主板设计更为薄身，就能够为 Apple Watch 的其他零件提供空间，包括容量更大的电池。</p><p>虽然没有明确指明是哪款型号，预计下一代 Apple Watch X 就会改用树脂涂层铜主板，因此在设计上出现重大改变。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/apple_watch_series_x_rcc_motherboard_material-news-62602.php">gsmarena</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/22/huawei-watch-fit-3-apple-watch-clone/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为 Watch Fit 3 谍照曝光，外媒狠批复制 Apple Watch 外观设计</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/apple-watch-touch-issue/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Watch 被指有「误触」情况，外媒：Apple 内部文件承认问题</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/03/watchos-11-to-drop-support-for-series-4/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">watchOS 11 将于 WWDC 公开   Apple Watch Series 4 或无法更新</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/apple-watch-x-rcc-motherboard-rumors/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/">Apple Watch X 结构改变，将采用较薄电路板物料</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
